<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(١٤٧٢)</span> وَحَدِيث: <span class="c1">" ركُوبه عَلَيْهِ السَّلَام فِي جَنَازَة ابْن الدحداح "</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(١٤٧٣)</span> وَحَدِيث: <span class="c1">" رَأَيْت النَّبِي - صَلَّى اللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّم َ - وَقد شمط مقدم رَأسه "</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١٤٧٤)</span> وَحَدِيث: <span class="c1">" إِنَّهَا لَيست الدَّوَاء، وَلكنهَا الدَّاء "</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>